text: Annette Solmell (born 1 July 1959) is a Swedish equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Norrköping
